{"tid":2489007,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"長實回購上限增至3.8億股 代價升至194億元","createTime":"2021-04-14T15:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T15:48:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1089aad2d16c040d6746807e199a15f57c22f0","tid":2489007,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:34:46.000Z","msg":"長實回購上限增至3.8億股 代價升至194億元<br />\n<br />\n長江實業(<a href=\"http://01113.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01113.HK&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sFc%2F7AvELiRjmt2A4bWGPaQ%3D&h=fafc9a29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01113.HK</a>)宣布，回購股份上限將會由333,333,333股，提高至380,000,000股股份，相當於已發行股份總數約10.29%，回購價維持每股51元，意味回購代價由約170億元升至193.8億元。<br />\n<br />\n長實指，修訂建議是根據股東的反饋而作出，旨在擴大公司對盈餘現金的調配，假設回購全面完成，與原計劃比較下已發行股份數目將出現淨減少，從而增加財務收益及提高資本回報，將對全體股東有利。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2387242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2F2387242&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sFc%2F7AvELiRjmt2A4bWGPaQ%3D&h=cffa22de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2387242</a>"},{"pid":"e1649a809ee611687c9290ff27788ec674712c89","tid":2489007,"uid":294423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 誠哥又然！公司回購變相基金會再增持。"}]}